  "texts": [
    "After agreeing to take part in the study, the participants were seated in front of a computer.",
    "Questionnaire used to measure the quality of the text.",
    "In the first phase, the participants were asked to rate the quality of all the text stimuli.",
    "Prior to rating the 20 stimuli, a training session with two training trials using two contexts and associated texts was shown to the participants.",
    "At the end of the training session, the participants were informed that they could now ask the experimenter any questions that they might have."
  ],
